THREE-WAY ACOUSTIC DESIGN – Smooth the connections among three drivers for excellent full-range sound which is more accurate and well-balanced;
    HIGH-FIDELITY SYSTEM – Consists of Isodynamic Ribbon Tweeter for rich detail sound and extend frequency range to 40kHz, 2’’ midrange to reproduce natural and sweet sound between 800Hz and 6kHz, and long-throw 6’’ woofer provides punchy and powerful bass playback;
    CLASSIC DESIGN – Luxurious solid wood cabinets aim to reduce resonance for high-quality audio reproduction; Sloping front panel is designed for stereo music listening;
    MULTIPLE CONNECTIONS – With various connection inputs in the cloud era, users can choose preferred connection method among Wifi, Bluetooth, Balanced XLR, LAN, and AUX;
    REMOTE CONTROL – Adjust volume and switch connection methods based on your personal preference for convenience.
